                  </hi> I am a widow, and live at 3, Princes-street, Woolwich. About three o'clock on the morning of the 18th of June, I was awoke by a policeman—I went down to my pigsty, and found that my pig was gone—I have seen it since, and can swear to it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470705-name-743" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-743" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
